hddtemp: hddtemp (monitor hard driver temperature)
hddtemp:
hddtemp: hddtemp is a small utility that gives you the temperature of your
hddtemp: hard drive by reading S.M.A.R.T. informations (for drives that
hddtemp: support this feature). This package also contains the device
hddtemp: database and the GkrellM 2 plguin.
hddtemp:
hddtemp: Note: Only recent hard drives have a temperature sensor.
hddtemp:
hddtemp: Packaged by Georgi D. Sotirov <gdsotirov@dir.bg>
hddtemp:
